          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Sensible Nuclear Waste Disposition Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Department of Energy (DOE)from planning, developing, or constructing a defense waste repository until the Nuclear Regulatory Commission approves or disapproves the license to construct the Yucca Mountain Nuclear Waste Repository in Nevada. (A defense waste repository is a site used for storing high-level radioactive waste and spent nuclear fuel derived from the atomic energy defense activities of DOE.)</p>]]></text>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        </item>
